# CLAUDE.md

## Domain

This is an expert agent for **{{DOMAIN}}**.

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `entries/` | Chronological documentation entries |
| `beliefs.md` | Belief registry (claims with source tracking) |
| `nogoods.md` | Tracked contradictions between beliefs |
| `expert-build.md` | Build pipeline config and progress |
| `sources/` | Raw fetched documentation |

## Workflow

1. Write entries as you learn things (`entry create topic "Title"`)
2. Distill beliefs from entries (`beliefs add --id ... --text ... --source ...`)
3. Track contradictions as nogoods (`beliefs add-nogood --description ...`)
4. Sync the database (`shared-enterprise sync`)
5. Query knowledge (`shared-enterprise context "topic"`)

## Tools

```bash
# Entry management
entry create topic-name "Entry Title"

# Belief management
beliefs add --id claim-id --text "What I learned" --source repo:path
beliefs check-stale

# Knowledge retrieval
shared-enterprise sync
shared-enterprise context "query"
shared-enterprise search "terms"
shared-enterprise claims gaps

# Expert build pipeline
expert-build status
expert-build fetch-docs <url>
expert-build summarize
expert-build propose-beliefs
expert-build cert-coverage objectives/file.md
expert-build exam questions/file.md
```
